(7/7)'

b'#GrowwDigest: Daily Highlights | 3 Sep 2020

\xe2\x80\xa2 Price of diesel cut for the first time in 6 months as the state-owned oil companies reduced the price of diesel by 16 paise. There is no change in the price of petrol. The current price of diesel in NCR is Rs.73.40 per liter.

b'#GrowwDigest: Daily Highlights | 3 Sep 2020

b'#GrowwDigest: Daily Highlights | 3 Sep 2020

\xe2\x80\xa2 Vodafone-Idea shares climb 30%

(4/7)'

(3/7)'

b'#GrowwDigest: Daily Highlights | 1 Sep 2020

\xe2\x80\xa2 AGR relief for telcos; Airtel stock up by 7% 
According to the Supreme Court order, the companies will be allowed 10 years to pay back the AGR dues starting from 1 Apr 2021. 10% of the total to be paid upfront on 7 Feb 2021.

(8/10)'

b'#GrowwDigest: Daily Highlights | 1 Sep 2020

\xe2\x80\xa2 August auto sales: Mahindra and Mahindra Ltd.
Total sales (domestic + exports) stood at 30,426 units in August 2020. This is a decline of 16%. Total exports fell 54% year-on-year to 1,169 units.

(7/10)'

b'#GrowwDigest: Daily Highlights | 1 Sep 2020

\xe2\x80\xa2 August auto sales: Ashok Leyland (Domestic + Export)
Total sales fell 31% year-on-year to 6,325 units in August 2020. Truck sales fell 36% year-on-year to 2,276 units. Bus sales fell 83% year-on-year to 313 units.

(6/10)'

b'#GrowwDigest: Daily Highlights | 1 Sep 2020

b'#GrowwDigest: Daily Highlights | 1 Sep 2020

\xe2\x80\xa2 August auto sales: @Maruti_Corp
